ag-voluntary-prayers-salat-nafilah","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-Wh","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/03\/nawafil-salat-separated\/","url_meta":{"origin":3613,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayers separated from obligatory prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyyah reported: When you perform the Friday prayer, do not pray another prayer until you have spoken or left the mosque. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, commanded us to do that, to not connect two prayers together unless we have spoken or we have left.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41205,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/salah-sitting-down\/","url_meta":{"origin":3613,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet prays sitting down","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, did not pass away until most of his prayers were performed sitting down, except for the obligatory prayers. Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 1653 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36227,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/21\/nafl-better-home\/","url_meta":{"origin":3613,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayers better at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Suhayb ibn al-Nu\u2019man reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe voluntary prayer of a man in his house is better than his prayer where people can see him, just as the prescribed prayers are better than the voluntary prayers.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 7322\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13043,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/23\/twelve-sunan-voluntary-prayers\/","url_meta":{"origin":3613,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Twelve voluntary Sunan prayers rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Habibah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs twelve cycles of prayer in each day and night, a house will be built for them in Paradise.\" Umm Habibah said, \"I have never abandoned them since I heard it from the Messenger of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},